      "content": "but it doesnt feel like space for something new. it just feels like... nothingness. if the essence of who i was—the part that actually made me feel alive—is gone, then what's left? it's just this biological machine performing tasks. i feel more like a ghost than a person. like the pilot has left and the plane is just drifting. how can there be a \"real self\" when the core of it is dead?",
